title: Acclaimed Trio Solisti to Perform at Adelphi University on Saturday, October 24 at the Performing ...
text: ( Source : Adelphi University ) Adelphi University is pleased to announce that the acclaimed chamber music ensemble Trio Solisti will be performing on Saturday, October 24 , at 8:00 p.m. at the Performing Arts Center , Adelphi University,
